If you previously had a Rookie Jockey and you fire him to hire an All-Star, your weekly Racing Limit will jump from 20 to 50.

 This is the same with downgrading Jockeys as well. If you had an All-Star Jockey and you fired him to hire a Rookie Jockey, your Racing Limit will drop from 50 to 20. 
<b>
If this causes you to be over your limit</b>, then you won't be able to Race until the refresh and your RU is reset back down to 0.</div></div>
