<h1>GUIDE TO THE TURFSIDE SPREADSHEET</h1><div class="whitebox">In Turfside, we use Google Spreadsheets to keep track of players and their horses. You can check it at any time to get updated information about your horses, money, inventory and more. If you are not familiar with Sheets, that's okay! The following is an explanation of our two most important tabs.</div><div class="mods-hh split-70"><div class="mods-column-ll">
<da:deviation id="7570399622825441">
</div><div class="mods-column-rr"><div class="purplebox"><h3>THE VAULT</h3>Player info is the 1st tab. Click on the image to zoom in.</div></div></div><div class="mods-hh split-70"><div class="mods-column-rr"><div class="purplebox"><h3>THE REGISTRY</h3>View your horses on the&nbsp; 2nd tab. Click the image to zoom in.
</div></div><div class="mods-column-ll">
