<div class="tealbox"><h5></h5><h5>Brief Overview of the other Tabs</h5>
<div class="col1"><h3>PUBLIC RACE WINNERS</h3>Log of horses that have won 1st, 2nd, or 3rd in a Public Race.
</div><div class="col1"><h3>BREEDING LOG</h3>Each horse has 15 breeding slots.&nbsp;The offspring IDs will be recorded here.
</div><div class="col1"><h3>NPC REGISTRY</h3>Group-owned NPCs are open to breeding with the public, each with a limit of 5 slots.
</div><div class="col1"><h3>TURFSIDE LOANS</h3>Low on coins? You may be interested in <a href="http://fav.me/dd8k061">taking out a loan</a>.
